### Variables
@host = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Create a New Company
POST {{host}}/companies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Corp"
}

### 2. Add an Address to a Company
# Note: Ensure companyId matches an existing ID from the previous request
POST {{host}}/companies/address
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": 1,
  "city": "Sofia",
  "street": "Vitosha Blvd"
}

### 3. Add an Employee to a Company
# Note: Ensure companyId matches an existing ID
POST {{host}}/companies/employee
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "companyId": 1
}

### Bonus: Hello World Check
GET {{host}}/hello
